## Development vs Production

### Development (with hot reload)

```yaml
services:
  app:
    build: .
    volumes:
      - .:/app
      - /app/node_modules  # Preserve container node_modules
    command: npm run dev
```

### Production

```yaml
services:
  app:
    build: .
    # No volume mount
    command: node dist/server.js
```
